{
  "text": "Explicit attitudes were assessed using seven-point semantic differential scales, which are psychometrically robust and have been used to assess explicit attitudes towards GM food in past studies (e.g. [CITATION_1] . Adjectives used to describe scale endpoints in the present study may be seen in Appendix 2.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "2128630"
